---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
import Button from "./Button.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="bg-light py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div data-animate>
      <SectionLabel text="What We Do" light />
    </div>

    <p
      data-animate
      class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-loose text-muted"
    >
      Quillmop is a content and digital marketing agency used by startups and
      enterprises to create strategic content, improve search visibility,
      optimise for AI answer engines, and drive measurable business growth.
    </p>

    <p
      data-animate
      class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-loose text-muted"
    >
      With Quillmop, your business gets sharp editorial expertise, proven
      marketing strategy, and intelligent content systems.
    </p>

    <h3
      data-animate
      class="mt-12 max-w-3xl font-display text-3xl text-dark lg:text-4xl"
    >
      Why not just use AI?
    </h3>

    <p
      data-animate
      class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-loose text-muted"
    >
      You can. But AI doesn&rsquo;t do the work, it assists with it.
    </p>

    <p
      data-animate
      class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-loose text-muted"
    >
      Every piece of content your business publishes still requires someone to
      identify the topic, do the research, write the brief, enter the prompts,
      evaluate what comes back, rewrite what doesn&rsquo;t work, edit for
      accuracy, refine the tone, check it against your brand, format it
      correctly, get it published, and more. That is the process for one piece
      of content. Your business needs dozens every month across your blog, your
      emails, your social channels, and your SEO strategy.
    </p>

    <p
      data-animate
      class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-loose text-muted"
    >
      One person can keep up with some of that, some of the time. A small team
      can cover more ground, but not without corners being cut, deadlines being
      missed, or channels going quiet for weeks at a time. The content that was
      supposed to build your business becomes the task that keeps getting pushed
      to tomorrow.
    </p>

    <p
      data-animate
      class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base font-medium leading-loose text-dark"
    >
      Quillmop is the team your business needs without the overhead of hiring one.
    </p>

    <div data-animate class="mt-8">
      <Button href={`${base}services`} variant="secondary" onLight
        >Learn More &rarr;</Button
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
